---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: Welcome Home
metaTitle: "Assisted Living & Retirement in Fayetteville, GA | Azalea Estates"
description: "Family-owned assisted living and retirement community in Fayetteville, GA. Independent living, assisted care, and respite stays on a 10-acre single-story campus with 24/7 licensed nursing."
eleventyComputed:
  heroImage: "{{ images.hero }}"
---

{% from "partials/icons.njk" import icon %}

<!--
  HERO — Background video
  Accessibility notes:
  • Autoplay works only when combined with muted + playsinline (mobile).
  • <video> is aria-hidden because it is decorative; the h1 + lead prose
    below convey equivalent information (WCAG 1.2.1).
  • A visible pause/play toggle satisfies WCAG 2.2.2 (Pause, Stop, Hide)
    for motion that runs longer than 5 seconds.
  • prefers-reduced-motion: respected via JS (starts paused on that OS setting).
  • <img> poster shown while the video buffers and if playback fails.
-->
<section class="hero">
  <div class="hero__bg" aria-hidden="true">
    <video
      class="hero__video"
      autoplay
      muted
      loop
      playsinline
      preload="metadata"
      poster="{{ images.heroPoster }}"
      tabindex="-1"
      aria-hidden="true"
    >
      <source
        src="https://cdn.rebelwarecdn.com/azaleaestatesfayetteville.com/videos/Sterling%20Azalea%20of%20Fayetteville%20Tour%20Video%20%40azaleaestatesoffayettevill8137.mp4"
        type="video/mp4"
      >
      {# Browsers that can't play MP4 will fall back to the poster image. #}
    </video>
  </div>
  <button
    type="button"
    class="hero__video-toggle"
    aria-label="Pause background video"
    aria-pressed="false"
    data-paused="false"
  >
    <span class="hero__video-toggle-icon" aria-hidden="true">
      <svg class="icon-pause" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><rect x="3" y="2" width="3.2" height="12" rx="0.8"/><rect x="9.8" y="2" width="3.2" height="12" rx="0.8"/></svg>
      <svg class="icon-play" width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 16 16" fill="currentColor"><path d="M4 2.2v11.6c0 .6.7 1 1.2.7l9.2-5.8c.5-.3.5-1 0-1.3L5.2 1.5C4.7 1.2 4 1.6 4 2.2z"/></svg>
    </span>
    <span class="hero__video-toggle-label">Pause</span>
  </button>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="hero__inner">
      <span class="eyebrow">Assisted Living &amp; Retirement · Fayetteville, GA</span>
      <h1>A graceful place to call home.</h1>
      <p class="lead">For more than thirty years, we&rsquo;ve welcomed seniors into a gracious, blended community of independent and assisted living &mdash; where every day feels a little lighter and a lot more like home.</p>
      <div class="hero__cta">
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn--primary">Schedule a Private Tour</a>
        <a href="/living-options/" class="btn btn--outline">Explore Living Options</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- STATS BAR -->
<section class="stats-bar">
